Paper: hep-th/9312180

Date: 1993-12-22

Title: Para-Statistics as Lie-super Triple Systems

Authors: S. Okubo

Comments: 29 pages, UR-1335, ER-40685-484

Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 35 (1994) 2785-2803

We first reformulate para-statistics in terms of Lie-super triple systems. Inthis way, we reproduce various new kinds of para-statistics discovered recentlyby Palev in addition to the standard one. Also, bosonic and fermionic operatorsmay not necessarily commute with each other.